o Fern\u00e1n G\u00f3mez]]. It was written by [[Fernando Fern\u00e1n G\u00f3mez]] [[Javier Garc\u00eda Maurino|Javier Garc\u00eda]] [[Maurino Fernando Morales]] and stars [[Pilar Bardem]], [[Jos\u00e9 Sacrist\u00e1n]], [[Chus Lampreave]], [[Mar\u00eda Barranco]], [[Agust\u00edn Gonz\u00e1lez]] and [[Tina Sainz]].\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|0166803}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:7000 dias juntos}}\n[[Category:1994 films]]\n[[Category:Spanish films]]\n[[Category:Spanish-language films]]\n[[Category:1990s drama films]]\n{{1990s-Spain-film-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Jmg38", "label": "safe", "comment": "8-year-old redlinks/mislinks", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/7000_d%C3%ADas_juntos"}
